    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk i checked online and some people said it might be lithium toxicity which sounds scary... but like my doctor always says to just drink more water if i feel weird. do u think i should just drink a ton of extra water and see if it goes away instead of making an appointment? i really dont want to go to the clinic if i dont have to",
